findings.title: Out of gas
findings.description: The function withdraw() uses a loop to transfer ERC721 tokens and could be aborted with OUT_OF_GAS exception if there will be a big number of tokens.

findings.title: Owner privileges (In the period when the owner is not renounced)
findings.description: The contract owner has excessive privileges to mint/burn tokens, change Factory addresses, positionsController address, and fee-related variables.
